g><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- OpenAI 本周推出了 ChatGPT Atlas，这是另一个 AI 浏览器，具有上下文感知、代理功能和内置\"记忆\"功能。Vite 团队公布了通过命令行开发工具 Vite+ 实现盈利的路径。Vercel 本周举行了两次会议：Next.js Conf 和 Ship AI。Next.js 16 发布，包含 Turbopack 改进、Next.js DevTools MCP 和 Cache Components 更新。Ship AI 涵盖了 AI SDK 更新、Vercel 的 AI Gateway 和 Agents 等内容。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.buzzsprout.com/2226499\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzsprout.com/2226499</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100060740\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"148\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=00398ee1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5dKoqRVWxW0W1LGKcqLJ6d11MfcAdGq5Dz6icMs1M7BKaKSlg2ldkOtRPTne3tnD2Q6nfhbfMbRpzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Whiskey Web and Whatnot：开源可能是你最好的职业选择 -- Shruti Kapoor</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 在 All Things Open 2025 录制，Robbie Wagner 和客座主持 Jason Lengstorf 与从开发者转型为内容创作者的 Shruti Kapoor 对话，讨论她从 Slack 和 PayPal 跳槽到 YouTube 的转变、开源的乐趣和陷阱，以及永恒的 Web 开发辩论。讨论了开源如何改变 Shruti 的职业生涯、贡献开源的真实价值、React Foundation 的重要性、React Conf 的亮点和新功能，以及从 Slack 工程师到独立内容创作者的转型过程。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\